The Government of Nepal has announced the suspension of all international flights from 2359 local time on 22 March, until 31 March.
If you’re a British National in Nepal and looking to travel to the UK, send your name, passport number, email address and phone number toBEKathmandu.Details@fco.gov.uk. We’re working closely with carriers and authorities to try to find a solution, and will contact you ASAPas soon as possible.
See additional advice on making travel plans to return to the UK, or what to do if you cannot depart immediately.
